comments: Jackson Jr. (MEM) jumps from point A to point B and initiates contact with Fox (SAC) that affects his driving shot attempt.
Sabonis (SAC) brings his hand forward towards LaRavia's (MEM) arm as he pursues the rebound, and the contact is marginal.
Sabonis (SAC) brings his hand forward towards Jackson's (MEM) lower body, and the contact is marginal.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) goes to, not through, Sabonis' (SAC) space and the off-ball contact is marginal.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) briefly grasps Sabonis' (SAC) arm, and the contact as the post entry pass is delivered is marginal.
Sabonis (SAC) grabs and pulls Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) jersey away from his body, which affects his post shot attempt.
Sabonis (SAC) is firming up over his left foot in LaRavia's (MEM) path and absorbs the contact during the screen.
Jackson (MEM) brings his hand forward towards Monk's (MEM) front, and the contact on the perimeter is marginal.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) grabs and pulls Sabonis' (SAC) jersey away from his body, which affects his ability to pursue the rebound.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) establishes position in the frontcourt prior to receiving the pass.
Sabonis (SAC) and Jackson Jr. (MEM) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Sabonis (SAC) is moving alongside Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) path, and the body contact that occurs during the driving shot attempt is marginal.
Aldama (MEM) cleanly deflects the ball away from Fox (SAC).
Sabonis (SAC) jumps forward into Aldama (MEM) and initiates body to body contact that affects his shot near the rim.
Jackson (MEM) clamps and holds Murray's (SAC) arm that affects his ability to pursue the rebound.
Sabonis (SAC) briefly grasps Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) left arm, and marginal contact occurs as Sabonis simultaneously deflects the ball away from Jackson Jr.
Sabonis (SAC) and Jackson Jr. (MEM) come together at the same spot, and the off ball contact is marginal.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) brushes Monk's (SAC) off-arm, and the contact during the shot at the rim is marginal.
Murray (SAC) has a resting hand on Bane's (MEM) body, and the contact during the driving shot attempt is marginal.
Sabonis (SAC) establishes himself in Jackson's (MEM) path and absorbs the incoming contact during the pick.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) is returning his foot to the floor and does not intentionally kick the ball away from Fox (SAC).
After Jackson Jr. (MEM) touches the ball, Fox (SAC) legally regains possession and resumes his dribble.
Murray (SAC) is moving alongside Bane's (MEM) path and the body contact that occurs as they come together during the drive is marginal.
Fox (SAC) legally contests Jackson's (MEM) jump shot attempt.
